body:
So my IGN is: sell bro for rp
feel free to add me if you have any questions that will not be answered below.

i obviously am looking for a ranked team, don´t rly care about rankings off others but i am plat V.
i´m teliing u now alrdy so that u know, i can only play in the evening also during weekend.
i´m 16 Yrs old,luxembourgish, but i can speak English,German and obviously Luxembourgish.
I´m looking for a constant team with constant teammembers,what i mean by that is that i want to play regularly and not have someone who is supposed to be in the team but then ends up never having time to play.
My mains are currently Tahm and Thresh but i can also play {{champion:432}} ,{{champion:89}} ,{{champion:201}} ,{{champion:12}} ,{{champion:267}} , as you can see my win ratio isn´t that high but that does not mean that i´m bad but only that it is very hard to carry as supporter:)
